<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.9.8">
<l>maiyārvari nīlammalark kaṇṇārmaṉam viṭṭiṭ</l>
<l>ṭuyvāṉuṉa kaḻalētoḻu teḻuvēṉkiḷi maṭavār</l>
<l>cevvāymoḻi payiluñciṟu puliyūrccala cayaṉat</l>
<l>taivāyara vaṇaimēluṟai yamalāvaru ḷāyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Releasing my heart completely from those with eyes</l>
<l rend="indent">like striped dark lily flowers,</l>
<l>To be saved, I began worshipping your feet; faultless one</l>
<l>Who dwells on a five-mouthed serpent couch on a watery bed in Ciṟupuliyūr</l>
<l>Where parrots practice words from girls’ rosy lips, be gracious!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
